V037B404   UMC_404   x037B402  (TL-)
V037B405   UMC_405   x037B402  (TL+)

V037B406   UMC_406   x037B403  (CL-)  (NO turbo, for 486SX 2X-OSC)
V037B407   UMC_407   x037B403  (CL+)  (NO turbo, for 486SX 2X-OSC)

NOTE!  Some 486 '481 REV-B parts crash with  Cache-Write "1 WS"  option,
       which UMC recommends at 16-33MHz.  (Part with problem observed
       is marked UM82C481BF, whereas earlier parts marked UM82C481B
       worked ok).

       The following BIOS versions suggest "2 WS" instead of "1 WS"
       for the default Cache-Write WS in the Setup Utility.

V037B40A   UMC_40A   486  REV-B (2WS)
V037B40B   UMC_40B   486  REV-B (2WS)  NO Turbo (for 486SX 2X-OSC)

V037B40C   UMC_40C   x037B40A  (2WS) (TL-)
V037B40D   UMC_40D   x037B40A  (2WS) (TL+)

V037B40E   UMC_40E   x037B40B  (2WS) (CL-)  (NO turbo, for 486SX 2X-OSC)
V037B40F   UMC_40F   x037B40B  (2WS) (CL+)  (NO turbo, for 486SX 2X-OSC)


